# flan-t5-retacred-all-kg-w-context-small-finetuned

[flan-t5-small](https://huggingface.co/google/flan-t5-small) finetuned over the TACRED Knowledge Graph patched with the [Re-TACRED proposal](https://github.com/gstoica27/Re-TACRED) (including negative samples) using the training method for [KGT-5](https://github.com/apoorvumang/kgt5/) with additional sentences alongside the prompts.
